title: PM 'desperate' to see changes in local football, says crown prince
text:
Prime Minister Najib Abdul Razak is “desperate” to see changes to the national football team and local league, according to Johor crown prince Tunku Ismail Sultan Ibrahim. 
Tunku Ismail said he met with the prime minister yesterday to discuss the matter.
